    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This property gives you access to the split view controller’s split view for querying its attributes or customizing it."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "By default, a split view arranges its child views vertically from top to bottom. To specify a horizontal (side-by-side) arrangement, implement the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nssplitview/1455318-vertical"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property of the split view object to return "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Also by default, a split view has a divider style of "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nssplitviewdividerstyle/nssplitviewdividerstylethin"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", and doesn’t have an autosave name."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "aside",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Don’t change the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": false,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nssplitview/1455306-delegate"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " property of a split view through the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": false,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nssplitviewcontroller/1388907-splitview"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " property of a split view controller, and don’t call any methods on the split view object using this property. If you do, the system raises an exception."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "style": "important"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "To provide a custom split view, set this property at any time before you call "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "super"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " in the inherited "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsviewcontroller/1434476-viewdidload"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method; that is, before the split view controller’s "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsviewcontroller/1434435-viewloaded"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property is "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The split view isn’t always the same object as that in the split view controller’s inherited "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsviewcontroller/1434401-view"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property. To access the split view, always use the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nssplitviewcontroller/1388907-splitview"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
